{"title":"山后的雪（外一章）","authors":["臧克家"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":5,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山后的雪（外一章）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山后的雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见了太阳要消融，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野蛮的农奴制，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能让它原封不动？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的母体上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疮疤要去净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地上一片光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能留个黑窟窿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已经五十多岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还清楚地记得儿时的事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“藏族、汉族是兄弟”写在小学课本上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头戴雪帽的喜马拉雅山高高在望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏，你在祖国辽远的边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人人心上投下个崭新的形象；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从各民族的声音里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听到了庄严和谐的大乐章。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}